Packages that use com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config
com.vernalis.pdbconnector This package implements the main KNIME node classes for PdbConnector. 
com.vernalis.pdbconnector.config This package implements (non-KNIME related) classes used to define the query and report options supported by the PDB advanced search and custom report web services.
